text.tspan: Atlas limits and statistics
Energy
Brain's temperature
Cold blood and reaction
Capacity of perspective
Multitasking
Every action needs a different
energy to be performed. In the macro
level, the energy used will depend from
the mass moved or the size of the wave
generated. In the micro level, energy
is quantized, so every action has a
specifical associated energy.
E
B.T.
Every action heats, depending on the energy used,
a little bit Atlas' brain. If its temperature reaches
the limit, he won't be able to act for while.
It could be cosidered as Atlas' level of calm.
The more this value lowers, the more Atlas'
reaction is slowed by its feelings.
The perspective on the world is
fondamental to understand his
own potential. Increasing this value
means that Atlas will be allowed to act
onto smaller orders of magnitude,
acquiring the capacity of dominate them.
Although he's able to shape the matter, is
perception is always human, so he needs to
understand a model of a small and
invisible level in order to act on it.
Multitasking is the ability to
perform more actions at the same
time without lose focus.
If this ability is developped, Atlas
will be able to separate the processes
in different tasks, until a limit of 8.
